replies.body:
Yi is still squishy with {{item:3053}} 
This build I gave above has armor and MR <100.  and around 2500 HP
you live for an extra 1 second, it doesn't give him God mode or something

Heh. This really wont change anything. Yi is going to keep his head down and keep farming. He is going to go on hit tank and defeat anyone in his way.
They can make champions have unique reloading mechanics, champs that crit every auto, champs that have the same ASpeed no matter what, champs that get carried by birds, but balancing a skinny dude with a sword is too difficult. 

fwiw, i have been playing tank yi for quite awhile and even with the titanic hydra nerf you are still going to be a force. You don't even have to build it. Prior to some item additions you could go
{{champion:11}} 
{{item:3111}} {{item:3931}} {{item:3153}} {{item:3071}} {{item:3742}} {{item:3102}} 
and be just as much of a monster
